title: Compound 2006 (DVD)
description:
Compound: Volume One  (skoterfilm)

\"Experienced video producer Clayton Stassart (formerly of Slednecks) and Slednecks team rider Chris Brown have teamed up to bring you a new generation of snowmobile videos entitled Compound Films. Sponsored and distributed by Slednecks, Volume One shows some of the most progressive freeriding to date, filled with big mountain riding, deep powder, huge cliff drops, and tons of airtime. This video is sure to please all.\"
